VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'trending number one repository of the day. PowerInfer is basically a CPU/GPU LLM inference engine leveraging activation locality for your device. I don\'t know what that heck that means. But basically, that means keeping the'

[10:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'actively used, the hot parts of the model constantly active and alive while putting some of the ones that are less commonly used to sleep. It\'s like a clever way of managing the model so that'

